ProcessEntity.Note:
This data group has the complete conversation (both from and to messages).

 

For separate the messages(from & to), use the following conditions,

 

If  "FromCustomer" data item value is not null then it is customer's sent message (sent items) and "ToCustomer" data item value is not null then it is customer's received message(inbox items)
